safeEthClose(address,uint256,address).details: Burn optionTokens and redeemTokens to withdraw underlyingTokens.

params.closeQuantity: Quantity of optionTokens to burn. (Implictly will burn the strike ratio quantity of redeemTokens).
params.optionToken: The address of the option contract.
params.receiver: The underlyingTokens are sent to the receiver address.

safeEthExercise(address,uint256,address).details: Swaps strikeTokens to underlyingTokens using the strike ratio as the exchange rate.

params.optionToken: The address of the option contract.
params.receiver: The underlyingTokens are sent to the receiver address.

safeEthMint(address,uint256,address).details: Conducts important safety checks to safely mint WETH option tokens.

params.mintQuantity: The quantity of option tokens to mint.
params.optionToken: The address of the option token to mint.
params.receiver: The address which receives the minted option tokens.

safeEthRedeem(address,uint256,address).details: Burns redeemTokens to withdraw available strikeTokens.

params.optionToken: The address of the option contract.
params.receiver: The strikeTokens are sent to the receiver address.

safeEthUnwind(address,uint256,address).details: Burn redeemTokens to withdraw underlyingTokens and strikeTokens from expired options.

params.optionToken: The address of the option contract.
params.receiver: The underlyingTokens are sent to the receiver address and the redeemTokens are burned.
params.unwindQuantity: Quantity of option tokens used to calculate the amount of redeem tokens to burn.

safeEthClose(address,uint256,address).notice: The redeemTokens to burn is equal to the optionTokens * strike ratio. inputOptions = inputRedeems / strike ratio = outUnderlyings

safeEthExercise(address,uint256,address).notice: Burns optionTokens, option contract receives strikeTokens, user receives underlyingTokens.
